adiy Volodos * Seymour Wakschal * David Walter * [[William Warfield]] * [[André Watts]] * [[Earl Wild]] * Paul Wolfe * [[Harold Wright (clarinetist)|Harold Wright]] * John Wummer * William Xucla' * [[Narciso Yepes]] * Miguel Zanetti * Richard Zeller * [[Mark Zeltser]] * [[David Zinman]] * [[Pinchas Zukerman]] * [[Michele Zukovsky]] {{ref end}}
